{
  "stem": "4695.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It gives them right away them to eat, and to drink, to give them red armbands with sticks.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And you will have the control of this-- of this Polish band.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "This was the first selection.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then they throw us a piece-- a few breads.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then--and we go.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The others, a day or two comes the other selection.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They give us a rest.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they tell-- they call us out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Polish soldiers, officers-- and maybe officers-- because they know not a lot Polish from Jewish ancestors, or Jews, step out.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I see a few hundred stepped out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But meantime, as a war prisoner, I come back with a friend what I was in the same sport club in two, as a younger boy.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we recognize each other.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we start like it was together in this.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And so I grabbed two Jewish boys.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "One name was Polivoda.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "A matter of fact, his brother maybe is alive here in Toronto.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the other was Dimenstein.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We was going together to the school, neighbors.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I grabbed them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I tell them, don't go out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And the other group who knows that I am Jewish, this is friend too, they tell, stay with us.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they cover us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But behind, I hear one of the Polacks, look-- and like to talk on the other boy, Dimenstein, this older are Jew.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And then the other from the two, quiet him down, and tell him, be quiet, because if not, I will quiet him down.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So everything was OK.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And the march route and march was very hard.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "It was raining.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
